"title": "8241: ethics, basis of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8241: ethics, basis of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The ultimate foundation of ethics is the character and will of God, which is made known supremely through Jesus Christ and in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>The foundation of ethics is the revealed righteousness of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:20\">ROM 1:18–1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:6\">PSA 97:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:14-Rom2:15\">ROM 2:14–2:15</a></p>\n<h2>The basis of ethics revealed in Scripture</h2>\n<h3>All Scripture</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:28\">LUK 11:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22\">JAS 1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:20\">PSA 103:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:17\">PSA 119:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6\">JHN 17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:8\">REV 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>The commandments of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:26-Deut11:28\">DEU 11:26–11:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:17\">JDG 2:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:29-2Chr34:31\">2CH 34:29–34:31</a></p>\n<h3>The will of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:35\">MRK 3:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:10\">PSA 143:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">COL 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>The commandments of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34\">JHN 13:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12-John15:17\">JHN 15:12–15:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:37\">1CO 14:37</a></p>\n<h3>The example of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:15\">JHN 13:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:2-Rom15:3\">ROM 15:2–15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:7\">ROM 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5\">PHP 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a></p>\n<h3>The ethical teaching of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p>In the Sermon on the Mount:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22\">MAT 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:28\">MAT 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:32\">MAT 5:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:34\">MAT 5:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:39\">MAT 5:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:44\">MAT 5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:29\">MAT 7:29</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:9\">JHN 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:18-John3:19\">JHN 3:18–3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:19\">JHN 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:48-John12:49\">JHN 12:48–12:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34\">JHN 13:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:22\">JHN 15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6\">JHN 17:6</a></p>\n<h2>Areas of life in which ethical conduct is expected of believers</h2>\n<h3>In sexual behaviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:26-Rom1:27\">ROM 1:26–1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:22-Lev18:23\">LEV 18:22–18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:1\">1CO 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>In government</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:21\">MAT 22:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:17\">MRK 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:25\">LUK 20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:11\">JHN 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:2-Rom13:5\">ROM 13:2–13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>In rewarding individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:7\">1CO 9:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In punishing individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:7\">GAL 6:7</a></strong></p>",
